title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E16 The Lobster Man
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea

S04E16
The Lobster Man

Airdate: January 21, 1968

    * One of 26 episodes from Season Four which have not yet been released on DVD
    * Remastered audio and video from VHS TV rip

The Lobster Man gets the crew of the Seaview in hot water.

Nelson: Richard Basehart. Lobster Man: Victor Lundin. Crane: David Hedison. Morton: Bob Dowdell. Kowalski: Del Monroe. Sharkey: Terry Becker. Sparks: Arch Whiting.
